message.body: No, I may be down tomorrow eve. I'm staying in tonight.
Ok. Sorry I haven't been in touch. Been pretty busy since my return. Want to see you, though. I'm working a double tomorrow, but might get cut early - say 9ish.
My friends are having a party tomorrow night (the house you went to with me last time.) If I'm not too fried after my double, I may go.
We are filming some stuff at the gallery tomorrow night so I probably can't make it but I like that crowd. We will have to do something soon though.
I would come to West Philly to see you tonight if I didn't have to work a double tomorrow. Maybe next week I can meet you there.
That sounds good. I'm beat today.
Ok, well let's definitely do it then. Tuesday night works for me. We can meet early, after you finish work. Just tell me where and when.
Ok that sound good to me. Have a good night
